item.description:
String concat with &lt;&gt;: &ldquo;Kiru&rdquo; &lt;&gt; &ldquo;.io&rdquo;
 concat list with ++: [1, 2] ++ [3, 4] results in [1, 2, 3, 4] hd [1, 2] == 1 tl [1, 2] == 2
  {3, &ldquo;ja&rdquo;} is a tuple
keyword lists, special list of two-element tuples [foo: &ldquo;bar&rdquo;, hello: &ldquo;world&rdquo;]
maps: %{:foo =&gt; &ldquo;bar&rdquo;, &ldquo;hello&rdquo; =&gt; :world}
maps-with-atom-keys: %{foo: &ldquo;bar&rdquo;, hello: &ldquo;world&rdquo;} == %{:foo =&gt; &ldquo;bar&rdquo;, :hello =&gt; &ldquo;world&rdquo;}
